{"tid":946487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美無證中國移民威脅校園屠殺 車上搜出步槍","createTime":"2018-12-18T14:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T03:19:59.000Z","uid":28765,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"40d0f707595193c7c0d5b459fb52a9077a56e0fe","tid":946487,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:21:47.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）一位逾期居留的中國移民，被控違法持有槍械及竊盜身分罪名，上周五認罪。<br />\n根據美國移民及海關執法局（ICE）網站，22歲的中國非法移民張翔宇（Xiangyu Zhang，音譯）住在德州拉馬克市（La Marque），在短期簽證到期後，逾期居留美國兩年。今年7月，他在美國退伍軍人事務部（VA）的網上聊天室，揚言威脅要殺害學童，引起ICE、國土安全部和美國煙酒槍炮及爆炸品管理局（ATF）的注意。張男並非美國的退伍軍人。<br />\n執法人員調查後，前往張男住家附近將他逮捕，當場在他車內查獲包括AM-15步槍等上膛槍械。國土安全部探員道森（Mark Dawson）：「相信根據張男做出的威脅，足以對社區造成危險。」<br />\n除了違法持槍，張男還涉嫌在擔任Uber司機期間偷走女乘客銀包、嘗試盜用信用卡購買蘋果產品、向美國銀行詐欺超過1.1萬美元。張男面臨最高10年徒刑、25萬美元罰款，預計於19日宣判判決結果。<br />\n美國移民及海關執法局  <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181218/59043466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181218%2F59043466&d=qAjeUnq431rM%2BBBwyK7HkRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=ab1c8582\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181218%2F59043466&h=ae82ee3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181218/59043466</a><br />\n<br />\n戰狼來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cba7555794226df78b80e8deaac39030dc725e5","tid":946487,"uid":511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"XYZ齊哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd82547c970c8d2d472cd94abb6ff6458f9fcbf4","tid":946487,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:03:21.000Z","msg":"靠犯咁大罪有得留低坐監<img src=\"/ass